data.title: Mr Herbert Asquith (Hansard)
data.text:
1852 - February 15, 1928

Constituencies

Fife Eastern July 1, 1886 - December 14, 1918

Paisley February 12, 1920 - October 29, 1924

Offices

Home Secretary 1892 - 1895

Chancellor of the Exchequer 1905 - 1908

Prime Minister April 5, 1908 - December 5, 1916

Secretary of State for War 1914 - 1914

Titles in Lords

Earl of Oxford and Asquith 1925 - February 15, 1928

Viscount Asquith February 9, 1925 - December 31, 1928

Contributions

First recorded, on March 24, 1887 RESOLUTION. Commons

By year, 15167 in total: 1887 1888 1889 1890 1891 1892 1893 1894 1895 1896 1897 1898 1899 1900 1901 1902 1903 1904 1905 1906 1907 1908 1909 1910 1911 1912 1913 1914 1915 1916 1917 1918 1920 1921 1922 1923 1924 1925 1926 1927

Last recorded, on March 22, 1927 NATIONAL EXPENDITURE. Lords
